text: Ani jara amhi yacya adhica tyanna azabadvare nasta karuna takale asate, tara khatrine ase mhanale asate ki he amacya palanakartya! Tu amacyajavala apala rasula (isaduta) ka nahi pathavila ki amhi tujhya ayatince palana kele asate, yapurvi ki amhi apamanita jhalo asato ani dhihkkarale gele asato
